Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.82,0:23:10.76,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&\fad(200,0)}喉通ったフレイバーには
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.76,0:23:16.79,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}初めて知る感情あふれ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.79,0:23:25.13,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}あこがれも傷も全て　今
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.13,0:23:32.81,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&\fad(0,200)}溶け込んで　光る
Dialogue: 2,0:22:16.57,0:22:22.32,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,水面の波紋から　顔逸らしたのは
Dialogue: 2,0:22:22.32,0:22:28.20,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,私の心　揺らいだの隠したくて
Dialogue: 2,0:22:28.20,0:22:34.13,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,あなたと並んでるだけの心臓が
Dialogue: 2,0:22:34.53,0:22:38.47,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}火照りやまない
Dialogue: 2,0:22:39.01,0:22:41.67,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}酔い　吐息　はにかんで
Dialogue: 2,0:22:41.67,0:22:44.93,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,柔い夢を見て
Dialogue: 2,0:22:44.93,0:22:47.64,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,袖触れて　満ち引いて
Dialogue: 2,0:22:47.64,0:22:50.60,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,目が合った
Dialogue: 2,0:22:50.60,0:22:53.53,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,奥底のまぶしさを
Dialogue: 2,0:22:53.53,0:22:57.36,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,一口味わうように
Dialogue: 2,0:22:57.36,0:23:02.78,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,名前を呼ぶ
Dialogue: 2,0:23:04.82,0:23:10.76,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}喉通ったフレイバーには
Dialogue: 2,0:23:10.76,0:23:16.79,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,初めて知る感情あふれ
Dialogue: 2,0:23:16.79,0:23:25.13,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,あこがれも傷も全て　今
Dialogue: 2,0:23:25.13,0:23:32.81,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}溶け込んで　光る
Dialogue: 3,0:22:16.57,0:22:22.32,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}水面的波纹上　那躲开的脸庞
Dialogue: 3,0:22:22.32,0:22:28.20,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}是我的心　想把荡漾藏起来
Dialogue: 3,0:22:28.20,0:22:34.13,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}只要与你站在一起　我的心脏
Dialogue: 3,0:22:34.53,0:22:38.47,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&\fad(0,500)}就炽热地跳个不停
Dialogue: 3,0:22:39.01,0:22:41.67,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&\fad(300,0)}醉颜　吐息　羞赧的你
Dialogue: 3,0:22:41.67,0:22:44.93,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}今晚做个好梦
Dialogue: 3,0:22:44.93,0:22:47.64,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}两袖相接　心潮涨落
Dialogue: 3,0:22:47.64,0:22:50.60,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}我看见你眼中的我
Dialogue: 3,0:22:50.60,0:22:53.53,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}就像要将深处的光芒
Dialogue: 3,0:22:53.53,0:22:57.36,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}浅尝一口那般
Dialogue: 3,0:22:57.36,0:23:02.78,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}呼唤你的名字
Dialogue: 3,0:23:04.82,0:23:10.76,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&\fad(200,0)}滑过喉咙留下的气味
Dialogue: 3,0:23:10.76,0:23:16.79,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}洋溢着从未有过的感情
Dialogue: 3,0:23:16.79,0:23:25.13,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&}憧憬也好　受伤也罢　如今全部
Dialogue: 3,0:23:25.13,0:23:32.81,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur5\1a&HFF&\fad(0,200)}融入其中　熠熠生辉
